    GeckoSession.PromptDelegate

    public static class GeckoSession.PromptDelegate.RepostConfirmPrompt
extends GeckoSession.PromptDelegate.BasePrompt
    RepostConfirmPrompt represents a prompt shown whenever the browser needs to resubmit POST data (e.g. due to page refresh).
